        "id": 1007275
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-03-19T17:35:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think it\u0027s fine to require people to write a wrapper closure for now. We can add a variants that accept a non-error-returning function (e.g. `PureFunc4v` or similar) in the future if it seems worthwhile.\n\nRenamed all to use a `New` prefix to align with `NewList` and friends.",
      "parentUuid": "655ce426_f796c25f",
      "revId": "065668779bc865ca3775c5b2702e4b079a79cf10",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
