      "writtenOn": "2026-03-13T18:03:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I can\u0027t see how this would be possible with the API I\u0027m proposing, given that it\u0027s possible to create a function independently of any field.\n\nMaybe the right answer is to avoid the options entirely and make the runtime better at keeping track of references and including the referenced name in the message.",
