      "writtenOn": "2026-03-19T17:35:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "As discussed online, we\u0027ll go with the current API for now: if impure functions are implemented, they might well have a different function signature anyway (for example they might take a context.Context argument).",
      "parentUuid": "9766cc9a_5dbfbc65",
      "revId": "065668779bc865ca3775c5b2702e4b079a79cf10",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
